llgal (0.8.1)

  * Add homepage to usage.
  * Fix captions reading regexps to (Thanks Samuel Mimram).
  * Fix captions reading which required two spaces before MVI/LNK/DIR captions.
  * Add more flexibility with only one space between two ----.
